norn (0.13.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  [ norn maintainers ]
  * BUG-003: fix norn peer connect (skip reqline encoding for just_dial)
  * FEAT-013: unit+SIT tests for peer-fetch IPC; coverage tracking
  * Debian package: restart user nornd daemons on upgrade
  * FEAT-014: DHT network lookup for bep44 get via IPC
    Add norn_dht_get_mutable() / norn_dht_get_immutable() synchronous
    wrappers; IPC handler now falls back to active DHT walk when local
    store misses.

